386
00:18:32.362 --> 00:18:34.989
I think I need it to calm
all the thoughts I have in my brain.

387
00:18:36.199 --> 00:18:39.118
Oh. sweet P.

388
00:18:39.202 --> 00:18:41.120
never feel like you need to stop that.

389
00:18:42.330 --> 00:18:44.707
