409
00:20:40.281 --> 00:20:43.493
From Greek mythology?
She's the goddess of the underworld.

410
00:20:43.576 --> 00:20:44.786
That sounds spooky.

411
00:20:44.869 --> 00:20:47.914
I guess my parents thought I was going
