417
00:21:02.720 --> 00:21:03.721
It's cool.

418
00:21:03.805 --> 00:21:06.432
They're cooler when
someone else gives you one. But...

419
00:21:06.516 --> 00:21:08.017
I don't really...

420
00:21:08.101 --> 00:21:10.395
Is that what your dad was saying.
